01:07:13.810 --> 01:07:20.700
So essentially think of writing
this in the following way-- 1

01:07:20.700 --> 01:07:31.220
minus eta of T1 and T2 equals
to 1 minus eta of T1 and T3,

01:07:31.220 --> 01:07:35.940
1 minus eta of T2 and T3.

01:07:35.940 --> 01:07:36.932
OK?

01:07:36.932 --> 01:07:40.410
The left-hand side
